item.title: Triple Moisture Silk Cream
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Our daily, salon-approved leave-in hair cream conditioner provides specialized care for extra dry, damaged hair. This nongreasy formula melts effortlessly, spreads evenly and absorbs quickly into strands, improving softness and manageability while diminishing fly-aways and frizz. It also has UV filters and is alcohol free. Three naturally derived extracts work on the hair strand to defy dryness: Olive penetrates to the center Meadowfoam Seed helps moisturize the middle Sweet Almond wraps the surface

HOW TO USE

  • Shake well.
  • Apply to damp or dry hair.
  • Dispense a small amount into palm, then spread between hands to form a thin layer.
  • Gently work cream downward through-out hair with fingers, concentrating on ends and outer layers
  • Do not rinse.
  • Style as usual.

item.title: Triple Body Oil massage
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Get smooth skin that looks silky with our award-winning lightweight sesame body oil moisturizer.This whisper-light formula absorbs quickly, locking in the moisture you need to achieve soft, smooth skin.

  • Available in Original and Fragrance-free
  • Olive penetrates to the center
  • Sweet Almond wraps the surface
  HOW TO USE
  • AFTER SHOWER OR BATH: While skin is still damp, smooth on a few drops to help seal in moisture. Let your body dry naturally, or simply pat dry with a towel.
  • IN THE BATH: Add to water and soften your skin while you bathe.
